\mt1 Seken Tesalonaeka  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip N…ôkuku…ô i Seken Tesalonaeka Pol r…®m…ôrai. In ramar…ô fwe Korin muv…ôrai raka Fas Tesalonaeka, m…ôkw…ô me nepw…®n h…ôukurau, n…ôn…ô in r…ôrhi pen s…ô i rev…ôn. N…ôrmama nepw…®n h…ôpkukur…ôn amasan mh…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Pol. Rer…®nraha r…®rhi m…ô Iesu truvehe akwauakw. N…ôn…ô ir…ôha h…ôpw…ôh wok s…ôv…ônraha mheitenhi Iesu. Pol r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô i m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôukur…ôn m…ô nuveheien s…ôv…ôi Iesu tr…ôfo ir…ô. In r…®ni m…ô tuham…ômwur ia noien wok meste Iesu truvehe.  
\c 1  
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rakupw…ôn  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt 1Tes 1:1\x*Iou Pol, Saelas, m…®ne Timoti.  
\p N…ôkuku…ô i rauvehe tukumiaha nakalasia me fwe Tesalonaeka.  
\p K…®miaha n…ôrmama s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo.   
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Rom 1:7\x*Pw…ôh Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha m…®ne I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo trou…ôriari pehe namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha.   
\s1 N…ô…°n…ô…°…®niien m…®ne n…ôfwakiien  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1Tes 1:2-3, 2Tes 2:13\x*Piak me, n…ôp…®n me pam k…®maha iaham…ôre…°i m…ô taham…ôkeikei mh…ôni vivi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha pam. Ratukwatukw m…ô tahamo iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n me pam nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha ruvehe mamskai mwi, n…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n me pam nokeikeiien s…ôk…®miaha kuatia kuatia hiamo m k…®miaha me ruvehe mamasori mwi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2Kor 7:4, 1Tes 2:19, Rev 1:9\x*Ro pen iaham…ôni irapw t…® nakalasia me s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ia kwopun me pam m…ô rer…®maha ra…°ien p…®k tukumiaha. K…®maha iaham…ôni iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n me pam hiam…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha, n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô n…ôrmama me kamhomet…ô k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô, mamho n…ômis…ôien me r…®p…®k m k…®miaha.   
\p
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Fil 1:28\x*Narimnari me i ramahat…ôn pen m…ô n…ôkiriien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn ratukwatukw a n…ôn…ô ro pen tuk…ôt…ô k…®miaha m…ô hi…ômwhen tih…ôuvnimw…ô ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ô Kumwes…ôn ram…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô. Kamo n…ômis…ôien m k…®miaha n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni t…® n…®t…ôt…ô n…ôha.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Rom 12:19, Rev 18:6-7\x*M…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn in ratukwatukw. N…ôrmama me i kamho n…ômis…ôien m k…®miaha, in tr…ôrpw…®n pen mwi n…ômis…ôien m…®nraha,  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Mat 25:31, 1Tes 3:13, 4:16\x*n…ôn…ô, muvei pehe napw…®sien m k…®taha m k…®miaha s…ôm…ôme hiamre…°i r…ôr…ôha. K…®taha ts…ôuvehi napw…®sien n…ôha n…ôp…®n tuk…ôtoni Iesu Kristo rier pehe ir…ô ir…ôha na…°elo skai me s…ôv…ônhi  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Sam 79:6, Aes 66:15, Rom 2:8, 1Tes 4:17\x*ia napw s…ô n…ô…°sen rasori. In tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôreirei Kumwes…ôn m…®ne n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôpw…ôh nesi penien n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ôv…ôi Iesu I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Aes 2:10,19,21\x*Ir…ôha tuh…ôuvehi n…ôrpw…®nien riti s…ô trouraha ir…ôha ia nuk nuk me fwe kwopun riti t…®pk…ôt…ô mh…ô n…ômri I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha ik…®n m…®ne nukuraanien ia n…ôsan…®nien asori s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Kol 3:4, 1Tes 3:13\x*Ir…ôha tuh…ôuvehi n…ôrpw…®nien n…ôha n…ôp…®n in truvehe ir…ô. Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha n…ôrmama ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi tuh…ô…°n…ô…°…®ni in. N…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ir…ô tuh…ôtoni in, n…ôn…ô n…ônimenraha trier. K…®miaha mwi tiho mwi iam…®nha ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hi…ôuv…ôni raka n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien s…ôk…®maha.   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Kol 1:9, 1Tes 1:2-3\x*N…ôp…®n me pam iaham…ôfwaki tukumiaha m…ô Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®taha tr…ôvsini k…®miaha m…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi. Iaham…ôres m…ô n…ôfe n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien amasan u…ô n…ôfe noien amasan ruku pen ia nahat…ôt…ôien hiokeikei m…ô tiho, in tro ir…ôha pam h…ôuvehe mh…ôuku…ô ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Aes 24:15, Mal 1:11\x*Ia noien n…ôha n…ôrmama tuh…ôuvehi ut…ô n…ô…°hi Iesu I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha tukumiaha, mh…ôuvehi ut…ô mwi n…ô…°h…®miaha tukwe resi pen namasanien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn s…ôk…®taha m…®ne I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo.   
\c 2  
\s1 I…ôrmama kani m…ô I…ôm…ô s…ô Ram…ôrui Loa  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1Tes 4:13-17\x*Piak me, ia n…®karen s…ôv…ôi nuveheien s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo m…®ne n…ôp…®n tukous…ôs…®mw…®n k…®taha ir…ô s…ôuv…ôn mh…ôtoni in, k…®maha iaham…ôres k…®miaha  
\v 2 m…ô tih…ôpw…ôh nehek…®r akwauakwien, mh…ôpw…ôh n…®re…°iien r…ôr…ôha tr…®ni m…®nu…ô hi…ôre…°i kani m…ô n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu ruv…ôuvehe raka. N…ôri au…ôr a m…ô tih…ôre…°i n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ruku pen t…® n…ôn…®mw…®n riti u…ô n…ôvisauien riti u…ô ia n…ôkuku…ô riti s…ô kani m…ô k…®maha iah…ôrhi pehe i tukumiaha.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt 1Tim 4:1, 1Jon 2:18, 4:3, Jon 17:12\x*Tih…ôpw…ôh n…ôseniien i…ôrmama riti reiku…ô ia k…®miaha ia suatuk riti iam…®nha ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ôp…®n n…ôha tr…®pkuvehe mh…ô meste n…ôp…®n n…ôha kam…®ni trukupw…ôn muvehe n…ôrmama tuh…ôsk…ômter mh…ôni …ôr…ôha Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô i…ôrmama n…ôha kani m…ô I…ôm…ô s…ô Ram…ôrui Loa tuk…ôtoni trier pehe, in n…ôha i…ôrmama s…ô tukouraha in.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Dan 11:36, Esik 28:2\x*N…ôp…®n trier pehe ir…ô, in tr…®ni …ôr…ôha pam narimnari me s…ôm…ôme kam…ôfwaki pen m…®nraha m…®ne narimnari me pam s…ôm…ôme kam…®ni kumwes…ôn ia nir…ôha. In truvehi ut…ô atukw a in ir…ônh…ô ia narimnari me n…ôha, muvnimw…ô m…ôkure ia n…ôkwai nimw…ô s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, n…ôn…ô m…®ni m…ô in Kumwes…ôn.   
\p
\v 5 R…ôfo? Hi…ônenouenou m…ô n…ôp…®n iak…®namar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha, iakam…®ni pehe narimnari me i tukumiaha?  
\v 6 N…ôn…ô hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka n…ôfe ramo tukuaha…° i…ôrmama n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni m…ô ia n…ôp…®n atukwatukw s…ôv…ônhi tuk…ôtoni in trier pehe.  
\v 7 Ipwet m…®ne n…ôrmama kamh…ôrui afafa raka Loa, m…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô ramo tukuaha…° ir…ôha m…ô tuh…ôpw…ôh noien ia kwopun rukuraan ik…®n, in tro iam…®nhi ir…ô meste Kumwes…ôn ruvehi raka in.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Job 4:9, Aes 11:4, Rev 19:15\x*Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha tuk…ôtoni I…ôm…ô s…ô Ram…ôrui Loa trier pehe. M…ôt…ô I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu tr…ôse …ôpune in ia n…®m…ôta…°i truku pen ia t…ôrhun. N…ôp…®n Iesu trier pehe ir…ô nuveheien s…ôv…ônhi trouraha i…ôrmama n…ôha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Mat 24:13, Rev 13:11-13\x*I…ôm…ô s…ô Ram…ôrui Loa truvehe mo narimnari me ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi Setan. In tro n…®mt…ôtien eiku…ô me, m…®ne narimnari me s…ôm…ôme kam…ôrk…ôrinari ir…ô,  
\v 10 m…®ne n…®feifeiien me s…ôp…ôms…ôp…ô s…ôm…ôme h…ôpkatukwatukw mh…ô. Ia noien n…ôha in treiku…ô ia n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamhesi pen suatuk s…ôv…ôi nemh…ôien. Kumwes…ôn trouraha ir…ôha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô kamh…ôni m…ô h…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ô rukur…ôn nuvehim…®ruien ir…ôha.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt 2Tim 4:4\x*T…® noien n…ôha s…ôv…ônraha, Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrhi pen n…®feifeiien skai riti t…® nir…ôha m…ô tro ir…ôha h…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia neiku…ôien.  
\v 12 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôrmama me pam s…ôm…ôme h…ôpk…®ni mh…ô n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien, m…ôt…ô rer…®nraha ra…°ien t…® noien s…ô r…®pkatukwatukw mh…ô, Kumwes…ôn tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha.   
\s1 N…ôkur Tesalonaeka tuham…ôkeikei mh…ôrer …ôknek…®n  
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt 2Tes 1:3, Jon 15:16, Efes 1:4, 1Tes 4:7, 5:9\x*M…ôt…ô piak me, I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha rokeikei k…®miaha. Ia n…ôp…®n me pam k…®maha taham…ôkeikei mh…ôni vivi Kumwes…ôn tukumiaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in r…®m…ôrfi k…®miaha fwe tui m…ô truvehim…®ru k…®miaha. N…ôn…ô in ruvehim…®ru k…®miaha ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi N…ôn…®mw…®n s…ôv…ônhi s…ô ro hi…ôuvehe mh…ômher, mho n…ôkur ikinan me s…ôv…ônhi, n…ôn…ô muvehim…®ru k…®miaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®miaha hi…ôni n…®p…ôrhienien ia n…ô…°kiariien p…ôrhien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 14 Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôkwein ia k…®miaha t…® narimnari me n…ôha ia n…ô…°kiariien amasan s…ô iaham…ôvisau irapw m…ô tih…ôuvehi p…ôri nasoriien s…ô I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo rauvehi fwe ia neiai.  
\v 15 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô, piak me, tih…ôrer …ôknek…®n, mh…ôkwt…ômhiri …ôknek…®n n…ô…°kiariien me s…ôm…ôme hi…ôuv…ôre…°i raka iahamahat…ôn k…®miaha ir…ô ia t…ôrhumaha m…®ne ia n…ôkuku…ô.   
\p
\v 16 Kumwes…ôn Tata s…ôk…®taha rokeikei k…®taha, mam…ôriari pehe namasanien s…ôv…ônhi m k…®taha. Ia n…ôp…®n me pam in rauvehi ut…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha, n…ôn…ô mamo k…®taha sam…ôre…°i ramasan t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô sam…ômri pen …ôknek…®n n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôk…®taha ir…ô. Iak…ôfwaki pen min m…®ne Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha mam…ôres m…ô irau  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1Tes 3:13\x*trouvehi ut…ô rer…®miaha n…ôn…ô rauo k…®miaha hi…ôskai t…® noien noien amasan m…®ne n…®niien n…ô…°kiariien amasan me pam.   
\c 3  
\s1 Kam…ôres n…ôfwakiien  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt 1Tes 5:25\x*Piak me, in i n…ô…°kiariien sampam. Tih…ôfwaki tukumaha m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha trev…ôn akwauakw ia kwopun me pam, n…ôn…ô, n…ôrmama tuh…ôsiai mhesi pen r…ômwhen a ia k…®miaha hiam…ôsiai mamhesi pen.  
\v 2 Tih…ôfwaki tukumaha m…ô Kumwes…ôn truvehi raka k…®maha t…® n…ôkur …ôr…ôha me, t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô komh…ô n…ôrmama pam kamhahat…ôt…ô ia Kumwes…ôn.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt 1Tes 5:24\x*M…ôt…ô k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn n…ôt…®…°iteien ia I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha. In tro k…®miaha hi…ôskai, n…ôn…ô m…ôtui amasan tukumiaha t…® Setan m…ô tr…ôpw…ôh nourahaien k…®miaha.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 2Kor 7:16, Kal 5:10, 1Tes 4:10\x*N…ôn…ô k…®maha iah…ôukur…ôn amasan ia n…ômri I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha m…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni n…ôha k…®miaha hiamo n…ôfe iaham…ôni, n…ôn…ô, tihamo iam…®nhi ir…ô mamh…ôuv…ôn.  
\v 5 Pw…ôh I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha triri rer…®miaha ia nokeikeiien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, mo hi…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia n…ôrerien s…ôv…ôi Kristo.   
\s1 K…®nise narpahaien  
\p
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Mat 18:17, Rom 16:17\x*N…ôn…ô t…ôkwt…ôkwuni piak me, iah…ôni pehe n…ôkwamaha tukumiaha i ia n…ô…°hi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo m…ô tiham…ôkeikei mh…ôrer isipw…®n t…® pi…ôvtaha me s…ôm…ôme kamharpaha, mh…ôpw…ôh nesi penien n…ô…°kiariien s…ô iah…ôn…ôv…ôha…° raka m k…®miaha ir…ô.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Fil 3:17, 1Tes 1:6\x*K…®miaha hi…ôuv…ôukur…ôn raka m…ô tihamo r…ômwhen a ia k…®maha. N…ôp…®n iah…ônamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha fwe kupw…ôn, iah…ôpkarpaha mh…ô.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt 1Tes 2:9\x*K…®maha iah…ôpkani mh…ô n…ôve…°…®nien s…ô i…ôrmama riti ruvei pehe au…ôr a m k…®maha. M…ôt…ô ia n…ôp…®n m…®ne ia ran iaham…ôsese mamhowok. Iah…ôpw…ôh nokeikeiien m…ô tah…ôuvei pehe wok skai m k…®miaha t…® n…ôkwm…ôniien k…®maha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 1Kor 9:4, 1Tes 1:6\x*Hi…ôukur…ôn m…ô ramasan a ko iah…ôres pehe nasituien iam…®nhi, m…ôt…ô iah…ôpko mh…ô. Iah…ôuvei pehe noien s…ôk…®maha m k…®miaha r…ômwhen ia noien riti s…ô tih…ôuvnhi.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt 1Tes 4:11\x*N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n iah…ônamar…ô k…®taha m k…®miaha, iah…ôuvei pehe n…ô…°kiariien i m k…®miaha m…ô, ‚ÄúTr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama r…ôpw…ôh noien wok, k…ôpw…ôh nuvehi penien n…ôve…°…®nien min.‚Äù   
\p
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt 1Tim 5:13\x*Iaham…ôni iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iahamre…°i m…ô n…ôrmama nepw…®n n…ôha ir…ôha kamhar…ô k…®miaha m…®nraha mamharpaha, mamh…ô…°kiari p…®k, mh…ôpko mh…ô wok.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 1Tes 4:11\x*Ro pen n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamho iam…®nhi ir…ô, k…®maha iaham…ôni pen t…® nir…ôha i, n…ôn…ô mamh…ô…°kiari skai m…®nraha ia n…ô…°hi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo m…ô tuham…ôkeikei mhar…ô afafa, mamho wok t…® nuvehiien n…ôve…°…®nien s…ôn…ônraha.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Kal 6:9\x*N…ôn…ô k…®miaha piak me tiho noien s…ô ratukwatukw mh…ôpw…ôh n…ôpouien i.   
\p
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1Kor 5:9,11\x*Tr…®ni m…®nu…ô i…ôrmama riti r…ôpw…ôh nesi penien n…ô…°kiariien s…ôk…®maha ia n…ôkuku…ô i, n…ôn…ô, tiham…ôkeikei mho pw…ôh n…ôrmama h…ôukur…ôn m…ô in sin. N…ôn…ô mh…ôpw…ôh nev…ônien ipaka tukwe pw…ôh raur…®s t…® noien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1Tes 5:14\x*M…ôt…ô tih…ôpw…ôh n…ômw…ôkiien i t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô in pi…ôvmiaha riti, n…ôn…ô ramasan m…ô tih…ôrpwi atukwatukw in.   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien sampam  
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1Tes 5:23\x*Pw…ôh I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôv…ôi n…ôm…ôrinuien in …ôpa truvei pehe n…ôm…ôrinuien m k…®miaha ia n…ôp…®n me pam ia noien me pam. Pw…ôh I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha tramar…ô tukumiaha pam.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1Kor 16:21\x*Iou Pol iakamrai n…ô…°kiariien i ia r…ô…°…®k mam…®ni ramasan tukumiaha. Ia n…ôkuku…ô me pam iakamrai iam…®nhi ir…ô m…ô tih…ôukur…ôn n…®raiien s…ôiou. In i n…®raiien s…ôiou iakamrai iam…®nhi ir…ô.  
\v 18 Pw…ôh namasanien s…ôv…ôi I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha Iesu Kristo tramar…ô tukumiaha pam.   